Current State (2025-08-20):
- AGENTS: 47 production agents with global access
- ORCHESTRATION: Tandem system with 85.7% success rate
- DATABASE: PostgreSQL 17 with >2000 auth/sec
- PROTOCOL: 4.2M msg/sec binary communications
- INSTALLATION: Multiple methods (full, LiveCD, portable)
- SYNC: Automatic 5-minute agent synchronization
- ACCESS: Global claude command from any directory

Key Features:
- claude-unified wrapper with permission bypass
- ~/.claude/agents/ symlink for Task tool discovery
- ~/.claude/orchestration/ for Tandem system
- Python venv support at ~/.local/share/claude/venv/
- Enhanced installers with dynamic path detection
- Comprehensive documentation and setup guides

